reviewText: Thanks! In time and the movie was brand new, as promised.

First, this edition does not include any subtitles
Second...El filme en si es maravilloso, son Bunuel, Figueroa, Silvia Pinal y otros miembros de la industria del cine mexicana haciendo su mejor trabajo. No hay perdida alguna.
Video y audio (no hay extras)
Supongo que es lo mejor que podia verse y oirse por un precio de menos de diez dolares...
No hay mucha calidad en estos renglones...

A group of well-hilled party-goers can't leave a room and a dinner had been turned into drama of self-exploring extended into a tragedy of miraculous exterminations.

Probably, it is a lesser-known original genre-example of a string of movies produced since 1962 outside Spanish-speaking world.
